GO WORLD ONLINE is new web site created
by Richard Bozulich of Kiseido.

You can log on by going to:

https://goworld-online.com

Access to this site is FREE!

Articles will be posted on a regular basis and
will cover all the tactical and strategic ideas
that arise in every phase of the game.

Each article is introduced by a short introduction,
encapsulating an important tactical or strategic idea.
It is followed by a problem or example illustrating that idea.

References are provided for follow-up study.

